h the inauguration has been delayed due to COVID-19, the school is currently open and available for community use according to their local guidelines. Additional plans to install a safe, clean water system near the new school in are currently underway. This facility in Antanapizina joins additional schools funded by Synergy throughout the region since 2016. The schools include: Besopaka, 1 school (2016), Ambohitrakongona, 1 school (2016), Farahalana, 1 school (2017), Antohomaro, 1 school (2017), Antsirabe Nord, 1 school (2018), Menagisa, 1 school (2018) and Ambolomadinika, 2 schools (2019).